TY  - JOUR
T1  - Capital Budgeting, the Hold-up Problem, and Information System Design
AU  - Arya, Anil
AU  - Fellingham, John
AU  - Glover, Jonathan
AU  - Sivaramakrishnan, K.
Y1  - 2000/02/01
PY  - 2000
DA  - 2000/02/01
